        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>prehistoric Northern Mesopotamian periods [300107696], prehistoric Mesopotamian periods [300107695], Mesopotamian (culture or style) [300019828], Near Eastern (Early Western World) [300019571], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
